%% Diagram: Event sourcing decision framework
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
graph TD
    A[Need event sourcing?] --> B{Audit trail or temporal queries critical?}
    B -->|No| Z[Stick with CRUD + audit table]
    B -->|Yes| C{Whole system or one bounded context?}
    C -->|One context| E[Hybrid: ES for that context, CRUD elsewhere]
    C -->|Whole system| D[Pure event sourcing]
    D --> F{Read-after-write consistency required?}
    E --> F
    F -->|Strong| G[Inline / synchronous projections]
    F -->|Eventual OK| H{Write throughput target?}
    H -->|High| I[Async projections + checkpointed subscribers]
    H -->|Moderate| J[Inline for hot read models, async for the rest]
